text: Myodocarpus angustialatus is provisional name for a threatened species of plant in the family Myodocarpaceae, which has not yet been formally described scientifically. It is endemic to New Caledonia. ==References== Category:Endemic flora of New Caledonia angustialatus Category:Vulnerable plants Category:Undescribed plant species Category:Taxonomy articles created by Polbot
